title: IAA Tonight | Will We Ever See Houston Harden Again?
description: James Harden has officially inked a new deal and will return to the Sixers for the 2022-2023 season. Will we see the James Harden of old that used to get buckets and dished dimes at will, or will we see the slowed down Harden that struggled to find his rhythym in Philly at the end of the season? Plus, Dodgers star OF Mookie Betts wore a shirt that said “We need more Black people at the stadium” when warming up for the Midsummer Classic at Dodger Stadium. What will it take to get more black people interested in baseball?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Brandon Marshall, Leger Douzable, Antoine Walker)
